<blockquote><div class=background></div><div class=copy>
<h1>
Circos Maps Cancer Landscapes
</h1>
<p>

<p>Nature features an article by Heidi Ledford, <a
href="http://www.nature.com/news/2010/100414/full/464972a.html">The
Cancer Genome Challenge</a>, which discusses the progress and
challenges of identifying structural variation signatures in cancer
genomes.

<p>Circos images are used throughout the piece, taken from the <a
href="http://www.sanger.ac.uk/genetics/CGP/cosmic/">COSMIC project</a>
(Catalogue of Somatic Mutations in Cancer).

<p><div class="ref_citation_brief"><span class="ref_id">6</span><span class="ref_author">Ledford H</span> <span class="ref_year">2010</span> <span class="ref_title"><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&db=PubMed&dopt=Citation&list_uids=20393534">Big science: The cancer genome challenge</a></span> <span class="ref_journal">Nature</span> <span class="ref_volume">464</span> (<span class="ref_issue">7291</span>) <span class="ref_pages">972-974</span>.</div>
</p>
<div class=annot>// cancer-genome-challenge</div>
</div></blockquote>
